Fields:

[emph]Title[/emph]

Text: the title of the item, e.g.: 'Nice poems to relax at lunch time'.
* Required field


[emph]Comments[/emph]

Textarea: some descriptive note.
E.g.: 
Both files are in UTF-8 mode, open them with an appropriate reader.


[emph]Project[/emph]

Select: parent Project which contains the Filemanager item, if none then select PHProjekt. 
* Required field


[emph]Upload[/emph]

This field allows you to upload one or more files.
Its way of work is absolutely intuitive: press the button at the right of the field, choose a file from your computer
and the file is sent.
Then the uploaded file appears behind the field with a cross button at its right side to delete it. The file itself is a
link to download it.


[emph]Tag[/emph]

The tag field that synchronizes the item with Tags panel.
